  "detailed_description": "<h1>Coming soon - Grunn!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Wamu Wamu 2 is a short experimental game about pieces of fruit that are infested by big worms, could you please clean them so they can be eaten? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206810/extras/3bfcf70944a7222c0b6388de45d5b095.poster.avif?t=1726497736\" width=280 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206810/extras/3bfcf70944a7222c0b6388de45d5b095.webm?t=1726497736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206810/extras/3bfcf70944a7222c0b6388de45d5b095.mp4?t=1726497736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Around 4-8 minutes of playtime.<br></li><li> Cute & colourful aesthetic with warm tones and soft gradients.<br></li><li> Use 3 different tools to clean 3 pieces of fruit.<br></li><li> It's very short, and weird, but funny?</li></ul><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Arrow keys to move.<br></li><li> Z to jump.<br></li><li> X to use tool.<br></li><li> C to switch tool.</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1206810/extras/c350ac25322f0cc81d29044611c576b9.avif?t=1726497736\" width=200 height=70 /></span><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ",
